  STRNADEL Josef. Statistical Model Checking of Approximate Circuits: Challenges and Opportunities. In: Proceedings of the 2020 Design, Automation & Test in Europe Conference & Exhibition (DATE). Grenoble: IEEE Computer Society, 2020, pp. 1574-1577. ISBN 978-3-9819263-4-7. Available from: https://ieeexplore.ieee.org/document/9116207 and https://www.fit.vut.cz/research/publication/12055/
